@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_alqynp(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (((v0 + 0.18 - tmp + 0.89) + (tmp + 0.54 * tmp + 0.58)) * wp.sin(wp.cos(v2 + 0.09)))
    v2 = wp.sin(v2)
    tmp = (v1 + ((tmp + 0.45 + v0 + 0.02) * wp.sin(v0 + 0.66)))
    v0 = (wp.abs(wp.sin(v2 + 0.05)) + wp.cos((v2 + 0.28 + tmp + 0.04)))
    data[tid] = v0
